## Introduction
This document outlines the review and proposed enhancements for the user interface and user experience (UI/UX) of the highly trafficked pages within the Forgotten Formula PMA member platform. The primary goal is to optimize the landing and member dashboard pages to better reflect our mission of placing healing over profits and nature over synthetic.


Our objective is to ensure that our digital platform provides an intuitive, seamless, and aesthetically pleasing experience for all members. This document provides a detailed assessment and recommended improvements following modern design principles and interactive flows, focusing on fostering a healing environment digitally.


